is about to give birth.

00:10:36.814 --> 00:10:38.094
Empress Dowager Chen Wanyi?

00:10:38.094 --> 00:10:39.054
She's still alive?

00:10:39.894 --> 00:10:40.614
Yes.

00:10:41.294 --> 00:10:42.654
She's about to give birth.

00:10:43.534 --> 00:10:44.934
What happened?

00:10:44.934 --> 00:10:46.694
(Even if she was pregnant,)

00:10:46.694 --> 00:10:48.254
(it's only been three months.)

00:10:48.254 --> 00:10:49.614
(How can she give birth?)

00:10:49.614 --> 00:10:50.814
(But she is alive,)

00:10:50.814 --> 00:10:52.014
(perhaps from her,)

00:10:52.014 --> 00:10:53.294
(I can find a different answer.)

00:10:53.814 --> 00:10:55.374
I don't know either.

00:10:55.374 --> 00:10:57.614
But Your Majesty instructed

00:10:58.294 --> 00:10:59.854
