00:11:06.334 --> 00:11:09.494
(Did I say something so wicked?)

00:11:09.494 --> 00:11:11.534
(Never mind, I'll go check it out.)

00:11:12.134 --> 00:11:13.134
Take me there.

00:11:13.414 --> 00:11:14.054
Yes.

00:11:39.814 --> 00:11:40.534
Get out!

00:11:41.134 --> 00:11:41.934
Get out!

00:11:45.454 --> 00:11:46.254
Get out!

00:11:47.134 --> 00:11:48.734
Get out of here!

